data.description: Welcome to the cutest country bungalow you've ever seen! This two bedroom, two full bath home is sitting on right at an acre. Home offers a nice living room kitchen combination, larger bedrooms and a full utility and laundry room. BONUS there is a fully finished building behind the house with drywall, electrical and water. You can use as a home office, man cave, hobby/crafting area, workshop, or a mother in law suite. There is also a shed for your storage needs. Enjoy having your own slice of country living but still in the heart of shopping, restruants, close to the beach and an easy commute to VA or Elizabeth City. Schedule your showing today!
